n compared to `Credit_History` in this model.\n4. **Final Model Choice:** **Logistic Regression** is chosen as the final model due to its high performance (80.5% accuracy, 0.801 ROC-AUC) and high transparency/interpretability.","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"","metadata":{"trusted":true},"outputs":[],"execution_count":null}]}